      "amount": "1/4 teaspoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "chopped fresh parsley",
      "amount": "1/4 cup"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a kazan cauldron over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chopped bell pepper and cook until it is tender.",
    "Add the cream corn, turmeric, paprika, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in the chopped fresh parsley.",
    "Serve hot."
